Cell["\<\
We have obtained,  
Provisional p - sig (E1) = (m,2m,3m)
Let be m=4n+k (k=0,1,2,3), then
         p-sig(E1)=(4n+k,8n+2k,3k+12n)
    Iso=p^n --\[Rule] p-minimal 
        p-sig(E1)=(k,2n+2k,3k)\[LineSeparator]    k = 0 -- -> (0, 2n, 0) -- n \
no 0 -> (0, \[GreaterEqual] 2, 0)-- > I_0
   k = 1 -- -> (1, 2n+2, 3)--> (1,  \[GreaterEqual] 2, 3)-- > III
    k = 2-- -> (2, 2n+4, 6) -> (2,  \[GreaterEqual] 4, 6)-- > I0^*
    k = 3 -- -> (3, 2n+6, 9)-- > (3,  \[GreaterEqual] 6, 9)-- > III^*
   \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8881433308879223`*^9, 3.888143374571212*^9}, {
   3.888143571828759*^9, 3.8881436034019003`*^9}, {3.8881436884055853`*^9, 
